<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_119" id="59r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_119_r2l19"> <expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan> Sweinfürt 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>weiſſemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></del> / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_119_r2l20"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde / Als <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Römiſch künig nu leıder <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> todes <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l21"><expan>abgange<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt das vns <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> leıd ıſt / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / was Jr ye trefflıchs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l22">
<del rend="strikethrough">etc </del> etc wöllen / vnd ob ew ſölıch ſache für kömen / darvmb ew dewcht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l23">daʒ wir die <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Stete 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒü vns manen vnſ </del> ewr vnd vnſer nachtge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l24">pawrn <expan>cʒeſam<ex>m</ex>en</expan> <expan>mane<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / das lıeʒʒet vns auch vviſſen / So <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l26">wir allweg <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein manung cʒü vns tün / Erfüren wir <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l27">ıht ſölıchs darvmb vns des not dewcht ſo <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_119_r2l25">wir </ab></add> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> manung </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l28">tün / . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_119" id="59r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan>, Sweinfürt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde, als <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> römisch künig, nu
                        leider <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> todes <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>abgange<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, das uns <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>rcze<ex>n</ex></expan> leid ist.
                            <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, was ir ye trefflichs etc. wöllen und ob
                        ew sölich sache für kömen, darumb ew dewcht, daz wir die
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> stete, ewr und unser nachtgepawrn,
                                <expan>czesam<ex>m</ex>en</expan>
<expan>mane<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>solt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das liezzet uns auch wissen, so
                                <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir allweg
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ein manung czü uns tün. Erfüren wir
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> auch iht sölichs, darumb uns des not
                        dewcht, so <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>wir</add>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> manung tün.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
